 was cast (like Earthquake does), the copy has the same value of X.£8/15/2010: You can’t choose to pay any additional costs for the copy. However, effects based on any additional costs that were paid for the original spell are copied as though those same costs were paid for the copy too. For example, if a player sacrifices a 3/3 creature to cast Fling, and you copy it with Reverberate, the copy of Fling will also deal 3 damage to its target.£8/15/2010: If the copy says that it affects “you,” it affects the controller of the copy, not the controller of the original spell. Similarly, if the copy says that it affects an “opponent,” it affects an opponent of the copy’s controller, not an opponent of the original spell’s controller.','R',NULL,'0.47','0.99','2.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','令其回响','令其回響','Réverbérer','Nachhallen','Riverberare','余韻','Reverberar','Реверберация','Reverberar','반향','瞬间','瞬間','Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント','Mágica Instantânea','Мгновенное заклинание','Instantáneo','순간마법','复制目标瞬间或法术咒语。你可以为该复制选择新的目标。','複製目標瞬間或巫術咒語。你可以為該複製品選擇新的目標。','Copiez le sort d''éphémère ou de rituel ciblé. Vous pouvez choisir de nouvelles cibles pour cette copie.','Kopiere einen Spontanzauber oder eine Hexerei deiner Wahl. Du kannst neue Ziele für die Kopie bestimmen.','Copia una magia istantaneo o stregoneria bersaglio. Puoi scegliere nuovi bersagli per la copia.','インスタント呪文１つかソーサリー呪文１つを対象とし、それをコピーする。あなたはそのコピーの新しい対象を選んでもよい。','Copie a mágica instantânea ou feitiço alvo. Você pode escolher novos alvos para a cópia.','Скопируйте целевое мгновенное заклинание или заклинание волшебства. Вы можете выбрать новые цели для этой копии.','Copia el hechizo objetivo de instantáneo o de conjuro. Puedes elegir nuevos objetivos para la copia.','순간마법 또는 집중마법 주문 한 개를 목표로 정한다. 그 주문을 복사한다. 당신은 그 복사본의 목표를 새로 정할 수 있다.','#_「还不错，不过我可以为它想出更好的用处。」_#','#_「還不錯，不過我可以為它想出更好的用處。」_#','#_« Pas mal, mais il me vient à l''esprit une meilleure utilisation. »_#','#_„Nicht schlecht, aber ich wüsste